* Neptune&#x27;s Known Satellites (by Scott S. Sheppard)
* Archival Hubble Images Reveal Neptune&#x27;s &quot;Lost&quot; Inner Moon (SETI : October 8, 2013)
* from NASA Jet Propulsion Laboratory</text><links>
